Class CQLWord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.mapping.CQLWord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CQLFragment, MappingToken

    public class CQLWord
extends Object
implements CQLFragment
    A CQL identifier (keyspace, table, column, named bound variable, etc).

    This class is merely a wrapper around the driver's CqlIdentifier that also implements CQLFragment.
